Zoeken naar Eileen (1987 - Netherlands)                  Looking for Eileen

Drama / Romance / Thriller
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0094382/


This romantic thriller is set in Amsterdam and centers upon a happily married, financially comfortable young couple whose lives are destroyed when the wife is killed in a car crash en route to London. The distraught husband falls into a deep well of despair. One year later his depression is lifted when he meets a woman named Eileen who is an exact double of his late wife. The husband becomes obsessed with her.
